[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "For with his eye he could not follow it So as to see aught else than flame alone, Even as a little cloud ascending upward,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "And the Leader, who beheld me so attent, Exclaimed: \"Within the fires the spirits are; Each swathes himself with that wherewith he burns.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Leave me to speak, because I have conceived That which thou wishest; for they might disdain Perchance, since they were Greeks, discourse of thine.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Thereafterward, the summit to and fro Moving as if it were the tongue that spake, It uttered forth a voice, and said: \"When I",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Joyful were we, and soon it turned to weeping; For out of the new land a whirlwind rose, And smote upon the fore part of the ship.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Three times it made her whirl with all the waters, At the fourth time it made the stern uplift, And the prow downward go, as pleased Another,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Already was the flame erect and quiet, To speak no more, and now departed from us With the permission of the gentle Poet;",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000077_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000077_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "But inasmuch as never from this depth Did any one return, if I hear true, Without the fear of infamy I answer,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000093_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000093_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Francis came afterward, when I was dead, For me; but one of the black Cherubim Said to him: 'Take him not; do me no wrong;",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000095_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000095_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "For who repents not cannot be absolved, Nor can one both repent and will at once, Because of the contradiction which consents not.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000100_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000100_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Onward we passed, both I and my Conductor, Up o'er the crag above another arch, Which the moat covers, where is paid the fee",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000118_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000118_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "\"Nor death hath reached him yet, nor guilt doth bring him,\" My Master made reply, \"to be tormented; But to procure him full experience,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000123_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000123_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "After one foot to go away he lifted, This word did Mahomet say unto me, Then to depart upon the ground he stretched it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000125_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000125_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Staying to look in wonder with the others, Before the others did his gullet open, Which outwardly was red in every part,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000140_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000140_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "But I remained to look upon the crowd; And saw a thing which I should be afraid, Without some further proof, even to recount,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000145_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000145_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "When it was come close to the bridge's foot, It lifted high its arm with all the head, To bring more closely unto us its words,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000165_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000165_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "When we were now right over the last cloister Of Malebolge, so that its lay brothers Could manifest themselves unto our sight,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000171_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000171_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "I do not think a sadder sight to see Was in Aegina the whole people sick, (When was the air so full of pestilence,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000185_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000185_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Wholly to me did the good Master gather, Saying: \"Say unto them whate'er thou wishest.\" And I began, since he would have it so:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000194_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000194_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "And Niccolo, who the luxurious use Of cloves discovered earliest of all Within that garden where such seed takes root;",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000202_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000202_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "He cried: \"Spread out the nets, that I may take The lioness and her whelps upon the passage;\" And then extended his unpitying claws,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000212_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000212_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "And he to me: \"That is the ancient ghost Of the nefarious Myrrha, who became Beyond all rightful love her father's lover.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000215_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000215_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "And after the two maniacs had passed On whom I held mine eye, I turned it back To look upon the other evil born.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000217_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000217_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "The heavy dropsy, that so disproportions The limbs with humours, which it ill concocts, That the face corresponds not to the belly,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000231_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000231_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "\"I found them here,\" replied he, \"when I rained Into this chasm, and since they have not turned, Nor do I think they will for evermore.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-81_121543_000246_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/81/121543/81_121543_000246_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-81",
        "content": "Such I became, not having power to speak, For to excuse myself I wished, and still Excused myself, and did not think I did it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]